response.overview: On November 24, 2017, Yonago Convention Center Big Ship in Yonago hosted Day 6 of NJPW World Tag League 2017.  The main event featured Los Ingobernables de Japon (BUSHI, EVIL, Hiromu Takahashi, SANADA & Tetsuya Naito) vs CHAOS (Kazuchika Okada, Will Ospreay & Gedo).  The card also featured Killer Elite Squad (Davey Boy Smith Jr., Lance Archer) vs Jeff Cobb & Michael Elgin.  Other wrestlers on the show include El Desperado, Minoru Suzuki, and Takashi Iizuka, and more!
response.title: NJPW World Tag League 2017: Day 6
